{"title":"getResource()获取中文或带空格路径问题报错处理","uid":"30348196f3e5c5edf9397c3928f42c56","slug":"Java/getResource()获取中文或带空格路径问题报错处理","date":"2021-09-07T04:33:42.000Z","updated":"2022-03-14T14:20:06.001Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Java/getResource()获取中文或带空格路径问题报错处理.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cover.png","content":"<h1 id=\"getResource-获取中文或带空格路径问题报错处理\"><a href=\"#getResource-获取中文或带空格路径问题报错处理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"getResource()获取中文或带空格路径问题报错处理\"></a>getResource()获取中文或带空格路径问题报错处理</h1><h2 id=\"1-问题描述\"><a href=\"#1-问题描述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 问题描述\"></a>1. 问题描述</h2><p>当我们使用getResource()获取文件路径时，路径中带有中文或者空格时，获取到的路径含%20字样。<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/49331b2f27fd4715bd3b5fecd4bc9643.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5YehMjIz,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>此时我们用该路径创建文件时报错，找不到该路径。<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/77d74471b1bd4a1cbf39d26ae8be01f9.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5YehMjIz,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>我们在资源管理器中复制该路径，发现确实找不到。<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/5ee2aac07ce84578a80e9e8b29afad54.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5YehMjIz,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>而我们将路径中的%20字样删除，转换为原本的空格，发现可以找到。<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/cec6a252ce5d4f0d81da89d829eadb90.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5YehMjIz,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"2-解决方案\"><a href=\"#2-解决方案\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 解决方案\"></a>2. 解决方案</h2><p>此时我们在getResource()方法后加一个toURL()方法，则不会报错，说明路径已成功找到。<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/de7f10bc962e41afb2731c3c498a05a1.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5YehMjIz,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>此时我们输出打印一下，%20字样消失，路径恢复正常，则可正常找到。<br><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/b9c3bfbd5ec44c2f925fdfce0d47dc20.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5YehMjIz,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br><strong>结尾：至此，问题成功解决。</strong></p>\n","feature":false,"text":"getResource()获取中文或带空格路径问题报错处理1. 问题描述当我们使用getResource()获取文件路径时，路径中带有中文或者空格时，获取到的路径含%20字样。此时我们用该路径创建文件时报错，找不到该路径。我们在资源管理器中复制该路径，发现确实找不到。而我们将路径...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":271,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":4,"path":"api/categories/Java.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":8,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#getResource-%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E6%88%96%E5%B8%A6%E7%A9%BA%E6%A0%BC%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">getResource()获取中文或带空格路径问题报错处理</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. 问题描述</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2. 解决方案</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"凡","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Fan223","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"https://weibo.com/u/6293437836","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/fan-ash","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/ACE_U_005A","juejin":"https://juejin.cn/user/4468879355285053","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Git总结","uid":"6307e383010802622c546f5e2b5cd218","slug":"Git总结","date":"2022-01-26T15:54:45.000Z","updated":"2022-04-1